  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/b6d64bedea46b547152ed2d5e64acac1.avif?t=1737707847\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >So someone finally bought the Ol' Grub, aye?</h2>Welcome, Bartender! <strong>Drinks Down Under</strong> is a Cozy Bartending Game where you bring an old bar back to life. Unlock unique ingredients, mix weird drinks and talk to strange customers as you progress through the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Turn this decrepit bar into the talk of town!</h2>Show your customers that The Clogs still have some shine to it! Give this bar a new name and a new coat of paint and learn your way through the recipe book the old owner left behind. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/023ef5328c3bcf1c0f1d0a642906b1e0.avif?t=1737707847\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the Big Shots!</h2>Some of your customers are not to be trifled with. Make sure every patron is satisfied by serving them the best quality of drinks and obliging to any requests they have. However... when a patron gets rowdy... maybe some lessons need to be taught.<br><br>Some of these customers also have stories to tell and secrets to uncover. Listen to them carefully... you might have a bigger impact than you think.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See for yourself what makes The Underground unique!</h2>Down here, things work a little differently from life out in the sun! Use cockroaches, slugs, junk juice, and more to create Drinks from Down Under! Explore strange ingredients, mix unusual drinks and survive to see another day doing in The Underground.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/b6d64bedea46b547152ed2d5e64acac1.avif?t=1737707847\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >So someone finally bought the Ol' Grub, aye?</h2>Welcome, Bartender! <strong>Drinks Down Under</strong> is a Cozy Bartending Game where you bring an old bar back to life. Unlock unique ingredients, mix weird drinks and talk to strange customers as you progress through the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Turn this decrepit bar into the talk of town!</h2>Show your customers that The Clogs still have some shine to it! Give this bar a new name and a new coat of paint and learn your way through the recipe book the old owner left behind. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/727d8a95533048b5ab89b31ffb8f8e5b.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/023ef5328c3bcf1c0f1d0a642906b1e0.avif?t=1737707847\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the Big Shots!</h2>Some of your customers are not to be trifled with. Make sure every patron is satisfied by serving them the best quality of drinks and obliging to any requests they have. However... when a patron gets rowdy... maybe some lessons need to be taught.<br><br>Some of these customers also have stories to tell and secrets to uncover. Listen to them carefully... you might have a bigger impact than you think.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/1c6ea47d65b4b1222460a0f0f972961d.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See for yourself what makes The Underground unique!</h2>Down here, things work a little differently from life out in the sun! Use cockroaches, slugs, junk juice, and more to create Drinks from Down Under! Explore strange ingredients, mix unusual drinks and survive to see another day doing in The Underground.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.poster.avif?t=1737707847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.webm?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825350/extras/c5cb761e1243b68f5fe8b4a1fcf76a06.mp4?t=1737707847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
